


Dvect(2D)            GRASS Reference Manual             Dvect(2D)



NAME
     Dvect - Tool for viewing GRASS vector (digit) maps
     (D Language Tool)

SYNOPSIS
     Dvect name [color]
     Dvect [option=value] [option=value]

DESCRIPTION
     Dvect displays the vector map (in binary form) name in the
     current graphics window.  Options are:

     name=mapname
          Name of vector map to be displayed.
     color=color
          Color desired for drawing map.  Default color is white,
          if unstated.

BUGS
     This tool cries for massive upgrade including:
          1) Allowing different colors and textures for lines.
          2) Allowing different fill patterns and colors for
          areas.
          3) An associated program for identifying these options.

AUTHOR
     James Westervelt, U.S. Army Construction Engineering
     Research Laboratory



























